OL,3,CGreen Party claim victory in by-
OL,4,Celection unseating Labour stronghold
OL,6,FThe new MP for Gorton & Denton Hannah
OL,7,FSpencer says she wants to bring back
OL,8,Ftrust in politicians.
OL,10,FThe Green Party has pulled off a
OL,11,Fconvincing win to overturn a Labour
OL,12,Fmajority of more than 13,000 and claim
OL,13,Fits first North West MP.
OL,15,FHannah Spencer, a plumber and a
OL,16,FTrafford Councillor, was elected for
OL,17,FGorton and Denton, claiming 14,980
OL,18,Fvotes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
