OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772193822
OL,3,CGreen Party claim victory in by-
OL,4,Celection unseating Labour stronghold
OL,6,FReform UK's candidate Matt Goodwin got
OL,7,F10,578 votes, with Labour's Angeliki
OL,8,FStogia trailing on 9,364, down from
OL,9,F18,555 in the 2024 general election,
OL,10,Fwhen the turnout was similarly high.
OL,12,FConservative candidate Charlotte
OL,13,FCadden received just 706 votes, with
OL,14,Fthe Liberal Democrats getting 653.
OL,16,FThe turnout was 47.62%, with 36,903
OL,17,Fvotes cast.
OL,19,FHannah Spencer addresses the crowd as
OL,20,Fshe is announced as the new MP for
OL,21,FGorton and Denton.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
