OL,3,CGreen Party claim victory in by-
OL,4,Celection unseating Labour stronghold
OL,6,FLabour had faced a tough battle to
OL,7,Fsave the previously rock-solid Greater
OL,8,FManchester constituency in the face of
OL,9,Fa double electoral threat from both
OL,10,FNigel Farage's Reform UK and Zack
OL,11,FPolanski's Greens.
OL,13,FHannah Spencer apologised to customers
OL,14,Fwho have booked her in for plumbing
OL,15,Fjobs as she delivered her victory
OL,16,Fspeech.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
