OL,3,CGreen Party claim victory in by-
OL,4,Celection unseating Labour stronghold
OL,6,FThe Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,7,Fwinner joked: "Now to my customers,
OL,8,FI'm sorry, but I think I might have to
OL,9,Fcancel the work that you had booked
OL,10,Fin, because I'm heading to Parliament.
OL,12,F"And when I get there, I will make
OL,13,Fspace for everyone doing jobs like
OL,14,Fmine. We will finally get a seat at
OL,15,Fthe table."
OL,17,FShe continued: "We have shown that we
OL,18,Fdon't have to accept being turned
OL,19,Fagainst each other. We can demand
OL,20,Fbetter without hating each other. We
OL,21,Fcan do that together.
OL,26,@oD@OOUtD@AOUwD@KO]yD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
