OL,3,CGreen Party claim victory in by-
OL,4,Celection unseating Labour stronghold
OL,6,F"We ran a hopeful campaign, backed by
OL,7,Fthousands of volunteers and activists.
OL,8,FWe defeated the parties of billionaire
OL,9,Fdonors.
OL,11,F"We have shown that we don't have to
OL,12,Faccept being turned against each other
OL,13,Fat all."
OL,15,FPrior to the polls opening the Green
OL,16,FParty said they were "confident" and
OL,17,Fhad run "a fantastic campaign" -
OL,18,Fpitching themselves as the only option
OL,19,Ffor tactically-minded anti-Reform
OL,20,Fvoters.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@HO]xD@VOUxD@`O]yD@IOUyD@
OL,26,A^O]
