OL,3,CGreen Party claim victory in by-
OL,4,Celection unseating Labour stronghold
OL,6,FThe by-election, which took place on
OL,7,FThursday 26 February, was triggered
OL,8,Fafter previous incumbent Andrew Gwynne
OL,9,Fannounced he was retiring on medical
OL,10,Fgrounds.
OL,12,FThe former health minister was
OL,13,Fsuspended from the Labour Party in
OL,14,FFebruary 2025 over offensive Whatsapp
OL,15,Fmessages including antisemitic slights
OL,16,Fand jokes about a constituent being
OL,17,F"mown down" by a truck.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
