CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772193822
OL,3,CGreen Party claim victory in by-
OL,4,Celection unseating Labour stronghold
OL,6,FAmong the five larger majorities is
OL,7,Fthe one at Runcorn and Helsby that
OL,8,FReform overturned at a by-election in
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FThe largest Labour majority to be
OL,12,Foverturned at a by-election since 1945
OL,13,Fis 22,915, which was achieved by the
OL,14,FConservatives at Ashfield in
OL,15,FNottinghamshire in 1977.
OL,17,FYou can hear Talking Politics wherever
OL,18,Fyou get your podcasts, including Apple
OL,19,FPodcasts and Spotify, and watch every
OL,20,Fepisode on YouTube and ITVX.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
